</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">体验less.scss</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//简写</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">@</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">import</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">注释</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div>","tagOpen":"<template>","tagClose":"</template>"},"script":null,"scriptSetup":null,"scripts":[],"styles":[],"customBlocks":[]},"content":"![](/body/green_8.webp)\n\n@[pdf](https://file.iglooblog.top/pdf/%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8web%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A9.pdf)\n\n## 移动端特点\n\n### 移动端和PC端网页不同点\n\n- PC屏幕大，网页固定版心\n- 手机屏幕小，网页宽度多数为100%\n\n### 谷歌模拟器\n\n浏览器按`F12`打开调试模式，选择手机模拟器\n\n### 分辨率\n\n#### 屏幕尺寸\n\n屏幕尺寸指的是`对角线`的长度，一般用`英寸`来度量\n\n#### 分辨率\n\n- 物理分辨率(出厂设置)\n- 逻辑分辨率(软件分辨率)\n\n| 手机型号                | 物理分辨率 | 逻辑分辨率 | 比例关系 |\n| ----------------------- | :--------: | :--------: | :------: |\n| iPhone3GS               |  320*480   |  320*480   |   1:1    |\n| iPhone4                 |  640*960   |  320*480   |   2:1    |\n| iPhone5                 |  640*1136  |  320*568   |   2:1    |\n| iPhone7/8               |  750*1334  |  375*667   |   2:1    |\n| iPhoneX/XS/11 Pro       | 1125*2436  |  375*812   |   3:1    |\n| iPhoneXR/11             |  828*1792  |  414*896   |   2:1    |\n| iPhoneXS Max/11 Pro Max | 1242*2688  |  414*896   |   3:1    |\n| iPhone12mini            | 1080*2340  |  360*780   |   3:1    |\n| iPhone12/12 Pro         | 1170*2532  |  390*844   |   3:1    |\n| iPhone12 Pro Max        | 1284*2778  |  428*926   |   3:1    |\n\n### 视口\n\n```html\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n```\n\n## 布局\n\n百分比布局\n\n[flex布局](/article/66oyxjbe/)\n\n[grid布局](/article/pvf28khi/)\n\n[响应式](/article/ziygmgyz/)\n\n## 移动适配\n\n### 长度单位\n\n#### rem\n\n> [!note]\n>\n> 1rem=1html字号大小\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"22rem\"](passwordgloo/wrzojkgd/)\n\n#### Vw/vh\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"23rem\"](passwordgloo/kvm3wtsf/)\n\n### 媒体查询\n\n```txt\n@media(媒体属性){\n\t选择器{\n\t\tCSS属性\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"18rem\"](passwordgloo/15fr0gb8/)\n\n## Less/Scss\n\n### 注释\n\n```less\n// 单行注释\n\n/* \n    块注释\n    第二行\n    第三行\n*/\n```\n\n### 计算\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"11rem\"](passwordgloo/wbL38pm6/)\n\n### 变量\n\n#### less\n\n```less\n// 1. 定义. 2.使用\n@colora:green;\n\n.box {\n    color: @colora;\n}\n\n.father {\n    \n    background-color: @colora;\n}\n\n.aa {\n    color: @colora;\n}\n```\n\n#### scss\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"17rem\"](passwordgloo/9uog67nj/)\n\n### 导入\n\n```scss\n//less\n@import '体验less.less';\n//scss\n@import '体验less.scss';\n\n//简写\n@import '注释';\n```","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"移动端特点","slug":"移动端特点","link":"#移动端特点","children":[{"level":3,"title":"移动端和PC端网页不同点","slug":"移动端和pc端网页不同点","link":"#移动端和pc端网页不同点","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"谷歌模拟器","slug":"谷歌模拟器","link":"#谷歌模拟器","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"分辨率","slug":"分辨率","link":"#分辨率","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"视口","slug":"视口","link":"#视口","childre